videos.headline: Carter bounces outside for 16-yard UNC TD
videos.description: Michael Carter gets to the outside and runs into the end zone to give UNC an early lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Carter bounces outside for 16-yard UNC TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: UNC's Howell picks up his first rushing TD of the season
videos.description: Sam Howell takes the ball into the end zone himself for a 10-yard Tar Heels touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UNC's Howell picks up his first rushing TD of the season) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Would-be NC State TD turns into wild North Carolina INT
videos.description: NC State's Ben Finley throws the ball into the end zone, but it is bobbled and picked off by a diving Don Chapman.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (NC State's wide-open TD turns into wild UNC INT) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Finley connects with Emezie for 42-yard TD
videos.description: Ben Finley finds Emeka Emezie, who spins around a defender and gets into the end zone for a 42-yard NC State score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Finley connects with Emezie for 42-yard TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Howell hits Downs for 17-yard TD
videos.description: Sam Howell finds Josh Downs wide open in the end zone for a 17-yard UNC touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Howell hits Downs for 17-yard TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams pushes into the end zone for short TD
videos.description: UNC's Javonte Williams pushes himself into the end zone in traffic for a 1-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams pushes into the end zone for short TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams records second rushing TD of third quarter
videos.description: Javonte Williams pushes past defenders and gets into the end zone for a 5-yard UNC touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams records second rushing TD of third quarter) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams finds a hole and trots into the end zone for 27-yard TD
videos.description: Javonte Williams finds a wide-open lane and picks up his third touchdown of the 2nd half for the Tar Heels.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams finds a hole and trots into the end zone for 27-yard TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: NC State's Smith extends for nice TD grab
videos.description: Bailey Hockman makes a nice pass to Anthony Smith, who hauls in the touchdown grab.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (NC State's Smith extends for nice TD grab) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: UNC tallies six TDs in decisive win over NC State
videos.description: North Carolina racks up six total touchdowns in a 48-21 win over NC State.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (UNC tallies six TDs in decisive win over NC State) 2020/10/24 ESHEET SOTFULL
